primo_labs_desc: Primo Labs will function as a launchpad and innovation hub for new features, NFT utilities, and community experiments. Stay tuned for exclusive tools and early access to upcoming projects.
docs_welcome: In the sprawling landscape of guides and references that could easily lead you astray for ages, you will eventually discover by the final words that this is the official Primos Marketplace documentation.
docs_treasury_desc: A permissioned Solana marketplace integrated with the Magic Eden API: a 2% market taker fee plus a 5% creator royalty, and additional on-chain community (2.4%) and operations (1.4%) fees. All proceeds fuel a shared on-chain treasury—powering buybacks, boosting floor price, and building real community ownership through DeFi mechanics.
docs_governance_desc: Only verified Primos holders can access the marketplace, join and help shape a legacy on-chain. We’re not building a DAO—we’re building a cultural hub. A place for Latinos and crypto explorers to dive into DeFi, NFTs, gaming, memecoins, and everything Web3. Primos isn’t just about holding—it’s about owning the future.
docs_utility_desc:
The real utility is the community. Primos is built by us, for us—every trade, stake, and action contributes to something bigger. 
 Together, we shape what’s possible on-chain. Whether it’s new tools, features, or cultural moments—every move we make creates momentum. Think “play → build”—we earn by doing, and grow by building.
docs_open_source_desc:
Primos isn’t just a marketplace—it’s a door. 
 A gateway to the unknown: cross-world swaps, DeFi bridges, and tools that could unlock the chain for those who haven’t arrived yet. 
 Every move on-chain could reveal new possibilities. 
 We won’t say much… but what’s coming isn’t just for holders. It’s for those ready to build with us. 
 And those here from the beginning… they’ll know exactly what to do when the time comes.
primo_labs_stats_desc: The DAO explores DeFi opportunities, real-world asset investments, DePIN incentives and even memecoin adventures.
primo_labs_floating_title: The most dangerous primo in the world
primo_labs_floating_body: The most loyal ones? They keep showing up. No matter what. No fanfare, no promises—just presence. That’s Primos. Always there. Always holding it down.
